[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大乘集菩薩學論卷第十四",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "試鴻臚少卿宣梵大師賜紫",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門臣日稱等奉　詔譯2說阿蘭若品第十一之餘《寶積經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次阿蘭若行，若諸異生未得果者，見虎狼至勿生驚怖，當發是心：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我本詣此阿蘭若處，已捨身命，不應驚畏。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』為起慈心，遠離過失使無怖懼。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若虎狼斷我命根、噉我身肉，應起是心：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我得善利，以不堅身而當獲堅固。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復不能令噉我肉，豈彼虎狼得樂觸耶？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』以要言之，復次阿蘭若行，有非人來，若美若醜，不應愛樂亦勿損害。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有往昔見佛諸天來此阿蘭若比丘所起諸問難時，彼比丘如力所能隨所學法為諸天說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若有深問難時，阿蘭若比丘或未能答而不生恭敬者，應語彼言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今未得無學。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若我當勤佛教，時聞法已盡能通解答一切問。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今唯能得聞是法。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』乃至總略，若住阿蘭若處藥草樹林，尚不取著，云何為生、何等為滅？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是觀察，是身無我、無主宰、無作者、無受者，誰生誰滅？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "畢竟無有生滅之者。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是身亦復如是，譬若草木牆壁瓦礫，無我、無主宰、無作者、無受者，因緣和合故即生，因緣離散故即滅。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次於勝義中無有一法是生是滅。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」彼經又說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次阿蘭若行，應發是心：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115b28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『然我至此阿蘭若處獨無伴侶，若我所起善作惡作，爾時此有天、龍、藥叉、佛世尊等，知我深心俱為我證。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』又若住此阿蘭若中，以心不善自在游逸。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若至此極遠之處，獨無伴侶無親近者，無我無取，應如實覺；",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲尋、恚尋、害尋及餘不善法尋悉如實覺。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若我於此不異其眾樂處有情憒閙中者，即為欺誑天、龍、藥叉、諸佛世尊。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如所作，天、龍、藥叉不為呵厭，諸佛世尊悉皆歡喜。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」12 治心品1治心品第十二禪定波羅蜜多附論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此阿蘭若修是禪定，如《般若經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「修此禪定波羅蜜多者，得心不散亂，利諸眾生。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "起世間定彼尚亦然，乃至心散亂者皆不可得，況復阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故得心不散亂，乃至成證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」彼經又說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次須菩提！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初發心菩薩摩訶薩修禪定波羅蜜多行時，於一切相智相應作意則善入禪定。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若眼見色不取其相，亦不執取隨形妙好。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於眼根不修制止，則依邪妄損惱於餘惡不善心隨其流轉；",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "護眼根者制此令盡。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是耳所聞聲、鼻所嗅香、舌所了味、身所著觸、意所知法，皆不取相亦不執取隨形妙好。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於意根不修制止，則於餘惡不善非法之心隨其流轉；",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "護意根者制此令盡，則行住坐臥語默時處，悉不捨離三摩呬多，得彼手足不生動搖、口無雜言亦無戲笑、諸根不亂。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若身若心俱無妄失，三業寂靜，於顯密中如律儀道，乃至喜足易養易滿，善入行處遠離憒閙，於得不得無有高下等無差別。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0115c28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是苦樂毀譽、若讚不讚、若夭若壽亦無高下等無差別，若冤若親心常湛然，是聖非聖其聲無雜，於樂不樂猶如一相無高無下，等無差別超諸違順。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於自相空、如、不真實，則見諸法無生無滅。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃至廣說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a03_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "喜樂修習者遠諸懈退，而常作意者息除高舉，於此二種是所對治。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "《護國經》偈云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a05_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「無量俱胝劫，　　所有佛出世，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是大仙尊，　　剎那獲勝益，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遠離於放逸，　　解脫諸染欲。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此有為虛妄，　　如幻夢所見，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乖離非久住，　　諸愛亦不常。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如奮力營求，　　諸波羅蜜地，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至悟菩提，　　精進無疑惑。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」《大戲樂經》廣說偈云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「老病死苦，　　如火焰然，　　三有熾盛，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無適無莫。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　未離輪轉，　　常處愚瞑，譬若狂蜂，　　處罃器內。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　三界無常，如戲劇者，　　及秋空雲，　　旋生旋滅。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人命遷壞，　　過於山水，　　輕捷迅速，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如電飛空。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　虛天界城，　　遍三惡道，無明橫起，　　愛有所生。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如陶家輪，　　常樂美色，　　及妙音響，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "清淨香味，　　細滑觸樂，　　貪著此者，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如被囚縶。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　如鹿寄網，　　如猴被縛，常懷怖懼，　　作冤家想。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　此欲樂者，極多憂惱，　　如鋒銳刀，　　亦如毒藥。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智者遠離，　　如棄糞瓶，　　愚懵念著，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為怖畏因，　　及為苦本。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　愛有所纏，疾趣衰老，　　常樂欲者，　　怖無歸捄。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昔有聖人，　　了知此欲，　　怖如猛火，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如大淤泥，　　如持蜜刀，　　如避空劍。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又諸智者，　　了知此欲，　　如糞穢瓶，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如毒蛇首，　　如木耦驢，　　如塗人血，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如死狗頭，　　如惡冤家。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知此欲，　　譬水中月，　　如山谷響，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如鏡中像，　　如戲劇人，　　如夢所見。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此欲樂，　　智者了悟，　　如幻如焰，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如水泡沫，　　剎那而住，　　遍計所起，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虛妄不實。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　但謂盛年，　　任持色相，意樂此者，　　實愚夫行。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　及老病至，壞苦所吞，　　退失光澤，　　如竭河流。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "財力豐饒，　　庫藏盈積，　　愛樂此者，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "實愚夫行。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　或至匱財，　　後疾耗滅，遠離於人，　　如空園林。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如花果樹，　　愛樂人悕取，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貧窶衰老時，　　厭棄如鴝鵅。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "豐財壯色者，　　樂生和悅意，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貧窶衰老時，　　厭棄如死屍。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此衰老相，　　年邁極過朽，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如雷電火，　　焚餘枯槁樹。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此衰老可畏，　　亦猶朽故宅，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故牟尼尊，　　說速求出離。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若娑羅林，　　為藤蔓所縛，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如男女眷屬，　　枯乾速衰朽。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若溺泥夫，　　頓乏於勇健，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此老相亦然，　　趨捷無快利。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "老變形容醜，　　威雄勢力衰，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長別妙樂尋，　　趣死無光澤。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此百種病惱，　　固非安隱樂，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是相於世間，　　熾然如猛獸。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀若老苦病，　　是世間苦惱，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "俱捨妙樂尋，　　說速求出要。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如霜與雪，　　奪草木滋茂，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "病苦於世間，　　壞命根色力。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "倉庫多崇積，　　追求極邊際，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常如疾病人，　　好起瞋恚事，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及冤害讎對，　　炎熱如空日，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及至死滅時，　　財命俱散壞。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬川流不返，　　如菓葉墮樹，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦如河中梗，　　漂沈不自在，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨業果難停，　　獨去無伴侶。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此死滅之法，　　又若磨竭魚，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吞噉無量眾，　　如金翅食龍，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及獸王搏象，　　若猛火焰然，",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "焚燒諸草木。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又《教示勝軍大王經》說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬若四方有四山來，堅固精實周普連匝，狀一合成無有缺漏亦無間隙，是中空界地際一切動植悉歸磨滅，誰有踊躑而可逃避，及以勢力呪禁藥術財物等事而令退轉？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有四種大怖畏事亦復如是，誰有踊躑而可逃避，及以勢力呪禁藥術財物等事而能退轉？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為四？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂衰、老、病、死。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c24_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c24_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者衰勢來時摧逼興盛，二者老相現時摧逼少壯，三者病苦集時摧逼調適，四者死滅侵時摧逼壽命。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此復云何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦如師子為眾獸王，色相勇健皆悉具足，爪牙剛利入鹿群中，搏取其鹿隨應所欲。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0116c29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然鹿踊躑入猛獸口，無能為也。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "死箭射人亦復如是，縱使剛強無能逃越，無歸無救亦無投寄，節節支解、血肉枯竭、飢渴熱惱、張口大息、手足紛亂，於追求事悉無堪能，涎涕流溢便利不淨，塗污支體餘命漸滅。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "中有現前隨業緣起焰魔使者甚可怖畏，趣黑夜分於出入息最後而盡，唯己獨行更無伴侶，奄背此生倏往佗世，奔大險道入大黑暗，涉大曠野、趣大稠林、泛大溟海，業風飄墮所向冥寞曾無標記，餘無歸捄餘無投寄。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯法與法是歸是捄、是所投寄。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a11_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此善法者，如寒者得火、如熱者遇涼、渴者飲清冷水、飢者食珍美饌、疾病者遇良醫藥、怖畏者得強力伴，是為歸捄。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸善法有大勢力亦復如是，無歸捄者為作歸捄、無投竄者為作投竄。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故應知，有現無常者、現滅盡者，法爾如是，唯死怖畏。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a17_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王恃所為，悉非善法。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然此身者從昔已來縱加守護，及加瑩飾上妙飲膳恣情飽滿，及命終時未免飢渴逼惱而死。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是身者雖以種種可愛奇文侈服上妙細㲲，行住坐臥隨意嚴飾，及命終時穢惡不淨要當流出。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此身者雖以澡沐塗香粖香熏香妙花無量嚴飾，及命終時不久臭穢。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此身者后妃婇女眷屬圍繞，種種妓樂歌舞嬉戲，及諸僮僕悅意快然，及命終時未免怖畏及諸苦惱。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至若此身雖處宮殿臺榭樓閣戶牖軒檻彩繪嚴飾，種種花香及與燈明，屏幛幃幔床座茵褥，燒眾名香散諸妙花，寶瓶香鑪處處行列，及妙珠寶錦綺雜飾玩好之具，及命終時至塚墓間，骨肉毛髮膿血臭穢，屍臥地上都不覺知。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又此身者而常乘御象馬車乘，擊鼓吹貝作大音樂，張妙幰蓋執持扇拂，無量勇健象兵馬兵車兵步兵導從前後，百千官屬城邑人民叉手恭敬，不久要當屍臥車上，眾人荷挽出大城門，父母妻妾兄弟姊妹奴婢僕從作業使人心纏憂惱，頭髮被亂舉手拍頭悲咽哀慟咸歎苦哉，於我無捄無親無主，城邑人民銜悲瞻戀。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至塚壙間，或復為諸烏鳶鵰鷲狐狼野干之所食噉，乃至餘骨積薪所焚或󰱼於地，風雨曝露末為微塵散擲餘方。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』佛言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大王！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b13_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此身幻化終歸壞滅，一切諸行悉是無常。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』乃至廣說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此貪瞋癡等一聚煩惱，至若對治脩習，因是遠離。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故《寶雲經》說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「對治貪者，於起貪緣悉能遠離。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何名對治貪及起貪緣對治？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貪者若善了知，於起貪緣修不淨觀。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何名不淨觀？",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂若於身髮毛爪、齒皮膚血肉筋脈、骨髓肪膏腦膜、汗淚涕唾、咽喉心肺肝膽脾腎、生臟熟臟屎尿濃汁，菩薩於如是物而起觀察，則愚癡小兒顛狂不善知是物已猶尚不起貪愛之心，況諸智者。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為菩薩修不淨觀。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又如《般若經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b25_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修般若波羅蜜多行時，然於此身如實了知。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬若解牛之師及師弟子斷牛命已，復用利刀析為四分，若坐若立如實觀察。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117b28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修般若波羅蜜多行時亦復如是，然於此身地界水界火界風界如實觀察。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若耕夫或諸長者，滿治場中有種種穀，所謂菽麥稻梁脂麻芥子等。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有明目人分別視之，如實了知彼種種穀，此是菽麥、此是稻梁、此是脂麻芥子等。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修般若波羅蜜多行時亦復如是，然於此身從頂至足髮毛爪齒種種不淨之所充滿。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而菩薩如實觀察是身，唯有髮毛爪齒、頭目脂髓、肝膽脾腎、生臟熟臟眵，矃不淨等。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至若詣塚間觀種種相，謂所棄屍於塚壙間或經一日二日乃至五日，身體膖脹青瘀臭惡、皮穿肉潰膿血交流。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見是事已，我與此身亦復如是。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然此身者法爾如是、本性如是，如是法性曾未解脫。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修般若波羅蜜多行時，而於外身修隨所觀，乃至觀所棄屍於塚壙間或經一日二日乃至七日，為諸鳥獸烏鳶鵰鷲狐狼野干之所食噉，及餘種種螻蟻咂食。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見是事已，我與此身亦復如是。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然此身者法爾如是、本性如是，如是法性曾未解脫。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以要言之，又若觀所棄屍於塚壙間蛆蟲咂食、不淨臭穢。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我與此身亦復如是，餘如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至復次向悽慘道觀所棄屍，肉銷骨現筋纏血污。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我與此身亦復如是，餘如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次向悽慘道觀所棄屍，血肉都盡身骨相現，餘筋尚纏。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我與此身亦復如是，餘如前說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c25_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次向悽慘道觀所棄屍，唯有眾骨散擲異方，所謂頭骨足骨、腰骨背骨、頸骨臂骨等。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我與此身亦復如是，餘如前說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至復次善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0117c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修般若波羅蜜多行時，向悽慘道觀所棄屍，唯有骨在，風飄雨漬白若珂貝。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我與此身亦復如是，餘如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次善現！",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a02_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩修般若波羅蜜多行時，向悽慘道觀所棄屍，唯有骨在，經𭚄多年變異青色，如泥處地碎末為塵。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我與此身亦復如是，然此身者法爾如是、本性如是，如是法性曾無解脫。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以不淨觀對治貪者，則修慈觀對治瞋恚，此乃平等。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不樂觀眾生者，此或於一飲食發生愛樂，則於他妙樂悕求稱讚、無不愛樂。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慈者度貪欲因緣不著染愛，是義有三種。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "《無盡意經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「謂初發心菩薩修眾生緣慈，已習行菩薩修法緣慈，得無生法忍菩薩修無緣慈。",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」大乘集菩薩學論卷第十四",
        "from": "T32n1636_014:0118a15_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]